latest_revision.text:
Fusion 360 brings Industrial and mechanical design together in a single easy-to-use design tool. Start by using simple push pull commands to get just the right shape, or take a short-cut by bringing in one of your existing or scanned models. Then add the detail needed to make your design manufacturable.

Fusion 360 is a web based 3D CAD tool with builtin support for sharing designs.

Free for personal use during Beta testing, Fusion 360 is expected to have a $25/month subscriptin cost at launch.

[http://fusion360.autodesk.com/about fusion360.autodesk.com]
